object.customQuery:
select riskid, policykey, yearbuilt, roweffenddt from dbo.risk
where riskid in ('FP21871361-DTORisk-1', 'FP21407015-DTORisk-1')
and yearbuilt is not null
and roweffenddt ='9999-12-31 00:00:00.000';
